ref=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/xunhuan/\" class=\"innerlink\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-decoration-line: none;\">循环</a>，心为真我，肉身为假我，五蕴皆空，凡所有相皆是虚无。</p><p><br/></p>','2019-04-06 01:50:36','2f608a3346db4880abb09d3f219b665b','0342169ec6a14f75ad18fff140cb6341',35,0,0,0,0,0,'/upload/post/jsp/images/20190407/1554648671278006308.jpg'),('dd2eb5799fc54e3ea79a9c42d94228a7','bcad377989c440d98c3e900244cf7f6f',6,'NCAA决赛弗吉尼亚队史首冠 得州理工加时惜败','<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/upload/post/jsp/images/20190409/1554802128094082686.jpg\" title=\"1554802128094082686.jpg\" alt=\"YNCZ-hvntnkp6885010.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 北京时间4月9日，NCAA决赛在明尼苏达阿波利斯开打，弗吉尼亚大学以85-77击败了得州理工，史上首次夺冠。</p><p>　　亨特命中打进加时的三分，全场贡献27分6个篮板，凯尔-盖伊24分，杰若梅16分、8个篮板和9次助攻。</p><p>　　得州理工功亏一篑。卡尔弗15分、9个篮板和6次助攻，“意大利炮”莫雷蒂15分。替补出场的弗朗西斯17分，爱德华斯12分。</p><p>　　这场“TV”之战，无论哪支球队夺冠，都将是队史首次。两支第一次进决赛的球队相遇，这是40年来NCAA第一次。无论哪一队胜出，都将成为第36支夺冠的队伍。</p><p>　　双方都以防守出名，一路过关斩将，都将对手得分限制得非常低。</p><p>　　弗吉尼亚进决赛非常幸运。在总决赛中，盖伊在最后7秒得了6分，终场前0.5秒，一次有争议的判罚将他送上罚球线，他三罚三中，弗大才以1分险胜奥本大学，首次晋级决赛。</p><p>　　走到这一步，谁都不会再退缩。开场后，双方都展开铁桶般的防守。前两欠进攻，都是在30秒将到时出手，未能命中。在这种严防之下，两队想打到篮下都很困难，也没有轻松出手的机会。比赛打了7分钟，得州理工仍未能投中一球，只靠罚球得分，以3-9落后。</p><p>　　得州理工前8投全失，上半场还有12分49秒时，莫雷蒂终于为他们命中一记三分。而替补上场的弗朗西斯两度三分命中，得州理工突然外线爆发，打出一波13-4后，将比分追成19-19。</p><p>　　得州理工前16投5中，三分球9投5中，意味着两分球7投全失。外线打开后，内线总算出了机会，本节还有6分39秒时，欧文斯切入接球，双手暴扣，这是他们第一个两分球，将比分追成21-21。双方开始拉锯战，进入势均力敌的局面。杰若梅命中一记压哨三分，弗大才以32-29领先结束上半场。</p><p>　　上半场得州理工命中率只有34.8%，三分球12投5中，罚球10中8。莫雷蒂和替补出场的弗朗西斯各得8分。</p><p>　　弗大命中率也不高，只有39.3%，三分球11投5中，罚球4中3。盖伊得了10分，杰若梅8分。</p><p>　　在防守能力都很强的情况下，进攻更好的弗大逐渐占了上风。下半场打了近一半时，盖伊命中三分，弗大以53-43取得两位数的优势。莫雷蒂连续两次突破上篮得手，得州理工开始反击。</p><p>　　到目前为止，得州理工替补得了25分，而弗大的替补只得2分。替补发挥出色，这是得州理工还能勉强抗衡的一大因素。</p><p><br/></p>','2019-04-09 17:29:06','25e6d66fa6df4e6cb9fc0c180ab096d3','2e484940bda640aeb64cc7b4b73a0c97',21,0,0,0,0,0,'/upload/post/jsp/images/20190409/1554802128094082686.jpg'),('e32bb7164e0347db90211fb3a68729cb','bcad377989c440d98c3e900244cf7f6f',5,'偏见地图也有国际版本 各国人民眼中的世界是这样的','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/upload/post/jsp/images/20190517/1558086563021009796.png\" title=\"1558086563021009796.png\" alt=\"image.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.63em; margin-bottom: 1.8em; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(25, 25, 25); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif;\">在中国，网络上流行的“北京人眼中的中国地图”、“上海人眼中的中国地图”、“湖南人眼中的中国地图”等国内版本的“偏见地图”外，偏见地图也有国际版本。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 15px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">保加利亚摄影师绘制的《世界偏见地图》犀利又不失幽默：在美国眼里，中国是座大超市，泰国居然是妓院，印度洋是海盗洋。在法国人眼中，荷兰等于大麻。在德国人眼中，爱尔兰就是威士忌……</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 15px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">这不仅是本全球地域歧视与偶像崇拜图谱，还堪称一部各国趣味撕B简史，下面就一起来感受下来自全世界的满满“恶意”吧！</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 15px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">美国人眼中的世界</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/upload/post/jsp/images/20190517/1558086620369082258.png\" title=\"1558086620369082258.png\" alt=\"image.png\"/></p>','2019-05-17 17:50:37','36b04407892a41b19e981bc91c6e0ac1','e2186ec544304443b6aeba7fe9591b06',0,0,0,0,0,0,NULL),('e4113756f982482593278f60945d462a','c2b53583abc745c486860c9809fb0230',4,'华为','<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/upload/post/jsp/images/20190407/1554648729382039476.png\" title=\"1554648729382039476.png\" alt=\"p30_left_cn.png\"/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">意外败北后，美国人并不服气，认为韩国的第一名拿的名不副实，只能算作“公关把戏”。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这是因为韩国第一批5G手机用户是电信商紧急拉来注册的6位名人（包括韩国演艺明星和奥运冠军），韩国普通用户要等到4月5日（即原定推出日期）才能注册使用5G网络。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">而无论这场大战结果如何，中国企业的身影都无处不在：韩国通讯商LG Uplus采用的是华为的技术，而美国威瑞森电信则选择了联想Moto Z3手机成为5G载体。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><h2 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">韩国率先推出5G服务</h2><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在本周四（4月4日），韩国最大的手机网络运营商SK电信发表声明称，</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“4月3日晚间11点，韩国已启动5G网络，首批用户是代表韩国的6位社会知名人士。”</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">根据报道，这6位名人中包括了韩国EXO组合的2名成员，以及花样滑冰奥运冠军金妍儿等人。</p><p><br/></p>','2019-04-06 01:18:56','2f608a3346db4880abb09d3f219b665b','f9ecb5c57a2e487ca0055bb0a8283919',19,1,1,0,0,0,'/upload/post/jsp/images/20190407/1554648729382039476.png'),('f31f641b0a2a40e9b7d21e895aae13bc','c2b53583abc745c486860c9809fb0230',5,'那窗，那光，那人','<p style=\"margin-